reviewText: This is an enjoyable video for the hunting enthusiast. It contains some great footage, does not include a bunch of nuts screaming after each kill, and does show the effort needed to successful when hunting. I am not sure that every hunt was life threatening to the host, but some were. They are offered to the viewer in a tasteful way. All in all, an enjoyable way to spend some time.
Pretty cool film. Timely arrival and enjoyable experience over all! Great fun entertaining happy exciting suspenseful adrenaline rushing family fun
